---
// English home — spec v1.2 §四 minimum EN coverage
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="AegisRD — Making scams visible before they strike"
  description="AegisRD builds an anti-scam ecosystem: AegisTalk secure messaging with on-device AI scam detection, AegisTrans cross-device transfer, AegisID biometric identity. E2EE, 100% P2P, edge AI."
  lang="en"
  altPath="/"
  active="home"
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:70vh">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">🛡️ AegisRD</div>
      <h1>End-to-end encrypted<br /><span class="gradient">communication & transfer</span></h1>
      <p>
        A technology company where privacy is guaranteed by architecture, not policy —
        encryption on-device, AI running locally, content 100% peer-to-peer.
        Two flagship products: <b>AegisTalk</b> (anti-scam secure messaging) and <b>AegisTrans</b> (cross-device encrypted transfer).
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/en/aegistalk" class="btn-primary">💬 AegisTalk</a>
        <a href="mailto:contact@aegisrd.com" class="btn-ghost">Contact us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ecosystem">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">// ECOSYSTEM</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">One ecosystem, every link of the scam chain covered</h2>
      <div class="eco-grid">
        <div class="eco-card talk reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">Flagship</div>
          <h3>AegisTalk</h3>
          <div class="tagline">Anti-scam secure messenger</div>
          <p>End-to-end encrypted messaging & calls with a three-layer on-device AI scam engine. Real-time red-shield alerts before the script works.</p>
          <span class="eco-badge badge-dev">App stores — coming soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card vpn reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">New</div>
          <h3>AegisTrans</h3>
          <div class="tagline">Cross-device file & message sync</div>
          <p>Your personal encrypted workspace across phone, tablet and desktop. Files of any size, 100% peer-to-peer — our servers never see your content.</p>
          <span class="eco-badge badge-dev">Beta</span>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card pay reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">Identity</div>
          <h3>AegisID</h3>
          <div class="tagline">Device-independent biometric identity</div>
          <p>A 512-dimensional facial feature vector — no photos stored, accounts survive device changes, impersonation gets cryptographic proof.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card track reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">Core on-chain testing complete</div>
          <h3>AegisPay</h3>
          <div class="tagline">The last gate before payment</div>
          <p>Conversation-aware risk gating on a non-custodial architecture. AegisRD never holds customer funds.</p>
          <span class="eco-badge badge-plan">Launching with AegisTalk</span>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem"><a href="/en/aegistalk/pay" style="color:var(--accent)">Learn more →</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ai-engine">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">// FOUNDATION</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Privacy by architecture, not by policy</h2>
      <div class="ai-layers">
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l1">E2E</div>
          <div class="layer-info"><h4>End-to-end encryption (Signal Protocol)</h4><p>X3DH + Double Ratchet. Encrypted before it leaves your device — we couldn't read it if we wanted to.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l2">P2P</div>
          <div class="layer-info"><h4>100% peer-to-peer</h4><p>Content travels over WebRTC DataChannels directly between devices. Servers do signalling only — zero content relay, zero retention.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l3">AI</div>
          <div class="layer-info"><h4>On-device edge AI</h4><p>Rust + WASM inference running on your phone. The thing analysing your conversations is your device, not our cloud.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Bring the guard home</h2>
    <p>AegisTalk ships exclusively through the official App Store and Google Play.</p>
    <a href="/en/aegistalk" class="btn-primary">About AegisTalk →</a>
  </section>
</Base>
